OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and breezy start with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain then becoming drier
OL,7,Fand brighter in the west through the
OL,8,Fmorning. The Lothians and Borders will
OL,9,Fthen becoming dry and bright in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry night with clear
OL,13,Fspells at first. Some cloud will
OL,14,Fspread across from the west overnight
OL,15,Fgiving the odd light shower in places.
OL,16,FSkies clearing in the west later.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FA cloudy start in the east
OL,19,Fwith the odd shower but soon
OL,20,Fbrightening up. Otherwise it will be a
OL,21,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
